WeWork’s revenue for the most recent reported period shown in the document (the **six months ended June 30, 2021**) was **$1,191,331 (in thousands)**, i.e., approximately **$1.191 billion**. This is reported in **“SELECTED HISTORICAL FINANCIAL INFORMATION OF WEWORK — Consolidated Statements of Operations Data (Six Months Ended June 30, 2021)”** on **page 23**.  

**Caveats / limitations:** The document excerpt provides WeWork financials only through **June 30, 2021** in the “Selected Historical Financial Information” section; later interim periods are **not shown in the provided text**. (See **page 23**, same section.)  

**Confidence:** **HIGH** (directly stated on **page 23**).
